###The data and script are for root fungal community of T. repens and B. pinnatum under different landscape designs 
(fragmented or connected patches inside mesocosms).
### We submitted the manuscript to PNAS on the 10th of Feb, it was declined by editor with suggestion to tranfer to PNAS Nexus ###
### We submitted the manuscript to Ecology Letters on the 3nd of March, awaiting referee scores ###
### It was rejected by Ecology Letters on the 13th of April with comments from two peer reviewers ###
### We submitted the manuscript to New Phytologist on the 28th of April, awaiting referee scores ###

